Paper: hep-th/9906172

Date: 1999-06-22

Title: Fractional spin and the Pauli term

Comments: 1 pg, Latex, no figures

Journal-ref: Phys.Lett. B470 (1999) 119-120

It has recently been claimed that the inclusion of a Pauli term in (2+1)dimensions gives rise to a new type of anomalous spin term. The form of thatterm is shown to contradict the structure relations for the inhomogeneousLorentz group.